snippet.title: Necronator 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
Follow us on Facebook: www.facebook.com/togeproductions

Once again, war is upon us! Gather your troops and prepare for an epic battle!

This is the sequel of the popular real time strategy flash game Necronator.

Release Date: November 2011
Genre: Action | RTS | Fantasy
Developer: Toge Productions
Publisher: Armor Games
